  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.poster.avif?t=1692338480\" width=690 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.webm?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.mp4?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>This game is a <strong>challenge for brave people</strong>. A challenge worthy of a true <strong>Squidding Master</strong>.<br><br>Do you think you have what it takes to reach the top? <strong>PROVE IT!!</strong><br><br><br>In this adventure you will have to <strong>help a slippery squid to reach the stars</strong>. But be careful, because you may stumble and slip back to where you started. Prove your worth by leading this clueless squid to the top.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.poster.avif?t=1692338480\" width=690 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.webm?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.mp4?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.poster.avif?t=1692338480\" width=690 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.webm?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/049698f3965c80305d7fe319b611bd37.mp4?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>This game is a <strong>challenge for brave people</strong>. A challenge worthy of a true <strong>Squidding Master</strong>.<br><br>Do you think you have what it takes to reach the top? <strong>PROVE IT!!</strong><br><br><br>In this adventure you will have to <strong>help a slippery squid to reach the stars</strong>. But be careful, because you may stumble and slip back to where you started. Prove your worth by leading this clueless squid to the top.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.poster.avif?t=1692338480\" width=690 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.webm?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517560/extras/dbb5bd66579932e7208d7f2e1d5143eb.mp4?t=1692338480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
